Legacy of Kain: Bloodbound RPG ‚Äì Monster Entry: The Hylden

üëÅÔ∏è The Hylden
Type: Aberration / Demonic Entity
Origin: Banished Plane (Hylden Realm)
Nature: Living, sentient, and technologically-augmented beings
Alignment: Chaotic Malevolent
Threat Tier: Elite to Boss (Varies by form)

üìñ Lore
The Hylden are an ancient race of flesh-bound sorcerers, scientists, and demagogues once equal in power to the Ancients. When denied dominion over the Pillars of Nosgoth, they were cursed and banished into a sealed dimension. Their last act before exile was to curse the Ancients with vampirism, setting the stage for Nosgoth‚Äôs long descent into chaos.
Hylden are beings of pure will and corruptive drive, often manifesting by possessing hosts, building soul-fueled constructs, or leaking through spiritual fractures. They are immune to spectral manipulation and see themselves as the rightful inheritors of reality.

üõ° Stats (Base Possessed Hylden Form)
HP: 20
Damage Reduction: 2 (not affected by spectral or radiant damage)
Armor Type: Bio-tempered husk (Physical)
Attributes:
Might: 3
Wits: 2
Spirit: 4
Shadow: 3
Will: 4
Fury: 2
Skills:
Possession: 3
